edko]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|name=[[Aleksey Antilevskiy]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=13|name=[[Oleksandr Mihunov]]|nat=UKR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|name=[[Vladislav Vasiliev]]|nat=KAZ|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=15|name=[[Yegor Bogomolskiy]]|nat=BLR|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|name=[[Raman Stsyapanaw]]|nat=BLR|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|name=[[Vladislav Morozov]]|nat=BLR|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|name=[[Denis Grechikho]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|name=[[Artem Kontsevoy (footballer, born 1999)|Artem Kontsevoy]]|nat=BLR|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|name=[[Gheorghe Andronic]]|nat=MDA|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=24|name=[[Vital Hayduchyk]]|nat=BLR|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=26|name=[[Sergey Tikhonovsky]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=27|name=[[Igor Shumilov]]|nat=BLR|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=29|name=[[Yaroslav Oreshkevich]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=31|name=[[Maksim Chizh]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=34|name=[[Artsyom Pyatrenka]]|nat=BLR|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=35|name=[[Artem Denisenko]]|nat=BLR|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs player|no=50|name=[[Oleksiy Kovtun]]|nat=UKR|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=59|name=[[Illya Kalpachuk]]|nat=BLR|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=77|name=[[Abdoulaye Diallo (footballer, born 1996)|Abdoulaye Diallo]]|nat=SEN|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=78|name=[[Dmitry Sibilev]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=99|name=[[Bogdan Sadovskiy]]|nat=BLR|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n== Honours ==\n* '''Belarusian Second League'''\n** ''Winners (1):'' [[2017\u201318 Belarusian Second League|2018]]\n\n==League and Cup history==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n!width=55|Season\n!width=50|{{Tooltip|Level|League level}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|Pos|Position}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|Pld|Played}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|W|Won}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|D|Drawn}}\n!width=30|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!width=60|Goals\n!width=45|Points\n![[Belarusian Cup|Domestic Cup]]\n!Notes\n|-\n| 2018 ||style=\"background:#A3E9FF\"| 3rd ||style=\"background:g